&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-mysql" data-lang="mysql">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">如果没有安装则可以使用&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">`&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">apt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">`&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">安装&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">sudo&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">apt&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">install&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">zsh&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="配置-oh-my-zsh">配置 oh-my-zsh&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>执行脚本安装：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">sh -c &amp;#34;$(wget https://raw.github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -)&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>oh-my-zsh提供了一系列丰富的主题和插件，默认在&lt;code>~/.oh-my-zsh/themes&lt;/code>中可以找到。
要使其生效我们要修改&lt;code>~/.oh-my-zsh&lt;/code>——zsh配置文件。
修改&lt;code>ZSH_THEME&lt;/code>字段启用主题：
&lt;img src="https://BeyondSword.github.io/p/%E5%BC%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C-zsh-%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97/2022-08-12-15-38-13.png"
