data-flex-grow="147"
data-flex-basis="353px"
>
修改&lt;code>plugins&lt;/code>字段启用插件：
&lt;img src="https://BeyondSword.github.io/p/%E5%BC%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C-zsh-%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97/2022-08-12-15-31-35.png"
